      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HESAA LISTER (2) put the writing on the wall when a 3m third two back then came from a deeper draw to score at this circuit and distance last week. Had enough speed to lead from out wide last time so can take advantage of this low draw. KING COREY (4) scored back-to back wins at this circuit and distance last month and came from wider than this when fourth last week. Has speed so expect him to be prominent from this barrier. FLIGHT LOUTENANT (5) didn't win at his maiden campaign but was runner-up in three of five starts, two of them here. Hasn't raced for three-and-a-half months but may have developed further with maturity. CLASSICMAJOR (1) has been coming from much wider barriers of late and was a winner at this circuit and distance two back so can make an impact from the ace draw.",
